gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pacers 121, Hornets 116
gameRecap.subTitle: The Pacers defeated the Hornets, 121-116, in overtime. Myles Turner recorded 18 points, four rebounds, and two assists for the Pacers, while Ben Sheppard added 14 points and three steals in the victory. Brandon Miller tallied 20 points (5-7 3pt. FG) for the Hornets in the losing effort. The Pacers finish the NBA Preseason with a record of 2-2, while the Hornets finish 2-3.

gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 128, Suns 122
gameRecap.subTitle: Dalton Knecht put up 35 points (8-13 3pt. FG), and 20 of the Lakers last 22 points to finish the game, as the Lakers defeated the Suns, 128-122, in overtime. Anthony Davis added 35 points, 10 rebounds, and four assists for the Lakers in the victory, while Devin Booker (22 points) and Kevin Durant (19 points) combined for 41 points for the Suns in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 2-3 in the NBA Preseason, while the Suns finish NBA Preseason with a record of 3-2.
